<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The book was written by folklorist Alvin Schwartz. Depending on the addition you read the art is either Stephen Gammell (the original creepy art) or t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The book was written by folklorist Alvin Schwartz. Depending on the addition you read the art is either Stephen Gammell (the original creepy art) or the 2010 re-release with artist Brett Helquist.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
