    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3000828229" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3000828229" />
    <a title="Ginger" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14097149-ginger"><img alt="Ginger" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1593449448p2/14097149.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3000828229?book_show_action=true">Oct 10, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ginger" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ginger" href="/user/show/14097149-ginger">Ginger</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780060835194" href="/book/show/7104431-scary-stories-to-tell-in-the-dark">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14097149-ginger?shelf=2019">2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14097149-ginger?shelf=library-book">library-book</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3000828229" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5144815234378046321">This was fun! <b>Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark</b> was very nostalgic.<br/><br/>When I was around 13-years-old, I would sit around in a circle with my friends, the lights were off and one of us had a flashlight under our face. We would tell scary stories and try to be the best at getting the most screams. Brings back great memories, lots of laughs and plenty of SCREAMS!<br/><br/>This would be a fun and spooky book to read to your kids around this time of the year. It&apos;s not scary but spooky enough to get them to jump a</span>
  <span id="freeText5144815234378046321" style="display:none">This was fun! <b>Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark</b> was very nostalgic.<br /><br />When I was around 13-years-old, I would sit around in a circle with my friends, the lights were off and one of us had a flashlight under our face. We would tell scary stories and try to be the best at getting the most screams. Brings back great memories, lots of laughs and plenty of SCREAMS!<br /><br />This would be a fun and spooky book to read to your kids around this time of the year. It's not scary but spooky enough to get them to jump and scream. And if you can do it around a campfire, even better!</span>
  <a data-text-id="5144815234378046321" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


